        "content": "<p>Lean has a propositional extensionality axiom. Does it also have \"proof term equivalence\":</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">axiom</span> <span class=\"n\">pte</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"k\">forall</span> <span class=\"n\">P</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"kt\">Prop</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">forall</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">P</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>  <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
