    {
        "content": "<p>What I mean by \"it is built in\" is \"Lean treats proofs of a same proposition as equal <em>by definition</em>\". Look how the proof of <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/proof_irrel\">docs#proof_irrel</a> is just <code>rfl</code>, which means \"true by definition\"</p>",
